    "causal_summary": "Phase 002 of the FULL_ISOLATE_NO_MCP arc moves 13 lib .ts files from system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/{deep-loop,coverage-graph}/ into the deep-loop-runtime/lib/ peer skill scaffolded in phase 001. Uses git mv to preserve history; patches internal cross-imports inside the moved set so tsc --noEmit is clean from the runtime skill root. Downstream MCP handlers in system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/*.ts compile-break by design and are repaired by phases 003-005 (script shims, handler removal, tool schema removal, workflow YAML swap). DB file relocation for deep-loop-graph.sqlite is phase 003's job; phase 002 only relocates coverage-graph-db.ts so the schema owner moves with the rest of coverage-graph/.",
